name: Issue 02 - Chicago Nights Stay
description:
The second installment of 23BLVD revolves around and is inspired by Chicago. Releases August 2013. 

5.5" x 8.5". 70 PAGES. Special vellum inserts. 3-D elements. Each printed copy comes with its own anaglyph specs for 3-D viewing pleasure.

Main Squeezes:
Inebriated Brewing
Shelby Steiner
theWHOevers
STOCK Manufacturing Company

Featuring talents by:
Charlie Kane, Eric Gupana, KP, Nosaj Thang, Judson Bernardo, and Katrina Tarzian
